snippet.title: DCL - The Game - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Drone Champions League AG and THQ Nordic today announced the cooperation on releasing Drone Champions League The Game (DCL - The Game) in Winter 2019/2020 for PC and consoles (no handheld systems).

DCL - The Game will be the official videogame of Drone Champions League - the world's leading championship for professional drone racing teams. Fly the original tracks from DCL and experience Drone Racing like a professional pilot.
